description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if it is confirmed that Andrew Tate has left the European Union for any length of time between July 5, 2024, 12:01 AM ET, and July 31, 2024, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

In cases where Andrew Tate may have exited EU airspace on a plane, he must be confirmed to have exited the plane in a non-EU country for this market to resolve to "Yes".

If Andrew Tate exits EU maritime territory on a boat to international waters, this market may resolve to "Yes".

If it is not confirmed by the resolution date that Andrew Tate fled the EU, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source for this market will be a consensus of credible reporting.
